plot: Jo gets dumped by her boyfriend Slade. Lauri gets a ring. Lauri's son Josh moves into the town house but "breaks house rules" and is kicked out.

Jo continues to pursue an entertainment career and spend more time in LA. Lauri confronts Ashley about her messy townhouse and then finds out Ashley is not enrolled in college. Meanwhile, Jeana does a provocative guest appearance on Sirius Playboy Radio, Tammy makes a final decision about her current relationship and Vicki "surprises" son Michael, which he's not too happy about.—Anonymous
